OL,6,F"It's a shocking way to be treating
OL,7,Fpeople who are contributing so much to
OL,8,Fsociety and public services," said
OL,9,FCraig Harrison from Carers NI.
OL,11,F"We knew this must be happening in
OL,12,FNorthern Ireland, but we didn't
OL,13,Fappreciate the scale on which it was
OL,14,Fhappening," he added.
OL,16,FThere are currently around 48,000
OL,17,Funpaid carers in Northern Ireland who
OL,18,Fprovide at least 35 hours of care for
OL,19,Fa sick or disabled loved one.
