OL,6,FUnder carers allowance they can claim
OL,7,F#81.90 per week.
OL,9,F"People are allowed to bring in a
OL,10,Fsmall amount of extra income and still
OL,11,Fkeep their carers allowance payments,
OL,12,Fthat earnings cap at the minute is
OL,13,F#151 per week," Mr Harrison.
OL,15,FBased on the figures gathered through
OL,16,Fa Freedom Of Information request, Mr
OL,17,FHarrison told UTV: "On average, each
OL,18,Fof the overpayment is close to #1,500
OL,19,Fwhich is a significant chunk of what
OL,20,Fcarers allowance is worth over the
OL,21,Fcourse of a whole year
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G3/10
