OL,6,F"The rules around additional earnings
OL,7,Fin the carers allowance system are
OL,8,Fvery complex and very opaque and so
OL,9,Fwhat these figures really raise a lot
OL,10,Fof big questions about why the
OL,11,Fdepartment isn't identifying these
OL,12,Foverpayments when they are happening
OL,13,Fand stopping people from accumulating
OL,14,Fsuch enormous debts.
OL,16,F"The earning rules can be very
OL,17,Fdifficult to stay on top of when
OL,18,Fyou're already leading a life that is
OL,19,Fhectic due to unpaid caring.
