OL,6,FWhen asked if he believed the
OL,7,Foverpayments had been caused
OL,8,Fintentionally or inadvertently, Sinn
OL,9,FFein MLA Colm Gildernew said: "The
OL,10,Fscale of it and the extent of it would
OL,11,Fsuggest to me that this is as a result
OL,12,Fof a system that is not functioning
OL,13,Fproperly.
OL,15,F"I think that is much more likely to
OL,16,Fbe the case and i think thats the
OL,17,Fapproach that needs ot be taken by the
OL,18,Fdepartment and they need to engage
OL,19,Fwith people in a way that sets out all
OL,20,Fof their rights," he added.
