OL,6,FIn a statement, the Department for
OL,7,FCommunities said: "Overpayments of
OL,8,FCarers Allowance primarily occur when
OL,9,Fthe Department is not updated on
OL,10,Fchanges affecting a person's
OL,11,Fentitlement. Where overpayment occurs
OL,12,Fdue to Departmental error or delay,
OL,13,Fthen the Department will not pursue
OL,14,Frecovery.
